reviewText: I was unable to watch - the format was wrong for US.  I didn't see a notice letting me know it was for certain areas only.  Very disappointed.
These dvds did not load to any DVD player in my house... attempted to contact seller with no response!
These DVDs do not play. Don't purchase.
Would be great if they actually worked...DVD spits it out as soon as I put them in.  Trying to return them with no response. Dont waste your money.
